text: Carl Hjorth (15 July 1875 - 26 April 1949) was a Swedish fencer. He competed at the 1906 and the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1875 births Category:1949 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish foil fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1906 Intercalated Games Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
